# Bright Data Web Unlocker — Supabase Edge Function secrets.

# Required
BRIGHTDATA_API_KEY=
BRIGHTDATA_UNLOCKER_ZONE=

# Sold SERP rows older than this many days are dropped (default 90). Raise if 130point only surfaces older sales.
# BRIGHTDATA_SOLD_LOOKBACK_DAYS=90

# ── Sanity-check REST from your laptop (same key/zone as Supabase). Expect JSON, not HTML:
# Uncomment the curl lines (remove leading #) or paste into the terminal without #.
# If node -e prints "{}" for zone, BRIGHTDATA_ZONE was not set in that shell (JSON omits undefined).
#
# curl -sS -X POST 'https://api.brightdata.com/request' \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_API_KEY" \
#   -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
#   -d '{"zone":"YOUR_ZONE","url":"https://geo.brdtest.com/welcome.txt","format":"json","method":"GET"}' \
#   | head -c 400
#
# Use format=json so the response is wrapped JSON (`status_code`, `body`). format=raw returns the target bytes only (no wrapper).
# A working response starts with "{" and includes "status_code" and "body".
# Dashboard “test” / proxy traffic can succeed while REST returns HTML if the API key or zone in Supabase does not match what you use here.

# Async /unblocker/* needs customer id + zone. Easiest: copy the full proxy user from Unlocker → Access details:
# BRIGHTDATA_PROXY_USERNAME=brd-customer-hl_xxxxx-zone-your_zone_name
# (hyphens exactly: brd-customer- … -zone- … — no spaces.)
#
# Or set separately: BRIGHTDATA_UNLOCKER_ZONE = part after "-zone-", and
# BRIGHTDATA_CUSTOMER_ID = only "hl_xxxxx" (between brd-customer- and -zone-).
# If you pasted the full brd-customer-…-zone-… line into CUSTOMER_ID by mistake, we parse it when PROXY_USERNAME is unset.
#
# If neither customer nor proxy user is set, the app uses sync POST /request only (no async customer param).

# BRIGHTDATA_SYNC_UNLOCK=true   → always sync POST /request (no async).
# BRIGHTDATA_ASYNC_FALLBACK_SYNC=false → do not fall back to sync when async fails.

# Optional tuning — see sold_listings_brightdata.ts
#
# eBay bot / checkpoint HTML: enable one retry after a pause (fresh Unlocker attempt may use another exit IP).
# BRIGHTDATA_RETRY_ON_EBAY_BOT=1
# BRIGHTDATA_EBAY_BOT_RETRY_MS=8000
